reviewText: Absolutely Great.  All of his DVD's are good.

I cannot say enough about Art Wolfe...if you have never watched his work...you are in for a treat. I have all of his video...love him, love his work..i have given away his videos to a number of friends.
Everything I ordered I have watched it already; This is an attempt to pass on my love of good literature to the next generation

Nice piece of art, great team. Beautiful landscaps, places, and for every photo a story behind. In few words, nice videos.

Sergio
This is a great DVD I bought it for my Dad for X-mas. And we all loved watching it.
